ED L 321F.title: Reading and Writing in Content
ED L 321F.prereq_description: Graduate standing and enrollment in The Teacher Education Program.
ED L 321F.description: This course is designed to provide credential candidates with the knowledge and skills necessary to design and enact comprehensive English Language Arts instruction in self-contained, integrated and inclusive K-14 classrooms.
